title: NCAA Division III Men's Basketball Supported Programs by Institution
name: NCAA Division III Men's Basketball Supported Programs by Institution
description:
This dataset explores men's basketball at the D3 level in the NCAA. There are 409 institutions that sponsor men's basketball at the D3 level. This dataset maps them.

                              Source: http://web1.ncaa.org/onlineDir/exec/sponsorship?sortOrder=0&division=3&sport=MBB


                              Accessed on Jan 29, 2008
